A SCUNTHORPE woman has said she&apos;s got more energy and confidence after a superhuman weight loss achievement. 
 
After originally popping along to a Weight Watchers session in support of her friend, Lisa Kennington, 34, of Ashby, wasn&apos;t even looking for weight loss advice or expecting any success herself when she attended the group 10 months ago. 
 
In that time, Lisa has lost an amazing six stones after originally weighing 17 stones. 
 
