&quot;I am proud of myself,&quot; she said. 
 
&quot;It&apos;s really motivating to carry on when you lose weight and you look and feel better. 
 
&quot;When I was overweight I didn&apos;t realise the impact it was having, I have lots more energy, I&apos;m able to do more and I have more confidence in myself. 
 
&quot;I have been exercising – I&apos;ve joined a gym which is something I never thought I would do.&quot; 
 
